parameters: Finding this orange spark can give one a headache.
Look in the cave room where you barrel trapped a snake.
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.I guess Clare and Diana made it through. I don’t see how though.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeBaDe.Oh well. It’s no use for me to follow them now.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrAnOp.Damn. These are some tall rocky cliffs.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaEx.A good sign a cave entrance is near, but difficult to navigate in the dark.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrBaEx.We need to use a rock bomb...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrBaOp.But it’s too loud. We’ll attract unwanted attention.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeWoOp.Well, what the hell do we do now?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrAnOp.Be quiet. Don’t let it hear us.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrAnOp.Apparently Corn wasn’t a big enough meal for him.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiWoEx.We should find a way through. No reason to go back with that cat running around.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrBaEx.If we can wait till sunrise we should be safe to use the rock bomb to get through.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaEx.With Sofia’s team trapped I can’t imagine they will find us here.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "CrBaEx.Sun will be back up in 8 hours...");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "DiBaEx.Let’s start a fire. The red glow might keep the jaguar away.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "HeFrEx.I was heading back... but then I thought I heard bigfoot.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiShEx.It sounded like a female bigfoot. Didn’t it?");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiSaEx.I appreciate your determination 1Hero. But it’s too late at night.");
$gameVariables.setValue(21, "MiFrEx.Nonsense 1Hero. Just wait until morning. It’ll be far safer.");
